Name:Cursed Civilian
Desc:When the Cursed Civilian gets attacked by the werewolves, they will not die. Instead, the Cursed Civilian becomes a werewolf themselves and may wake up together with the werewolves on the next night. The Cursed Civilian awakes at the end of every night to view their own card - to learn whether they remain as a Cursed Civilian or if they have turned into a werewolf. The Cursed Civilian may not intentionally try to be turned into a werewolf.
